snippet.title: Behringer
snippet.description:
We Hear You.

We at Behringer believe in carefully listening to you and providing you with life-changing products at prices so you can fulfill your musical dreams. Major artists include Earth, Wind & Fire, Elton John, Foreigner, Living Colour, Symphony X, Bela Fleck, etc.

Founded in 1989, as a struggling musician and sound engineer, Uli Behringer couldn’t afford the necessary equipment for his own studio. Initially building products for himself only, he soon supplied them for his friends, too. This led to Behringer’s philosophy to deliver life-changing products at prices everyone can afford.

We obsessively focus on our Customers in the Live Portable Sound, Musician, Recording, DJ/EDM and Broadcast verticals.
Based in Willich, Germany, Behringer is an incredibly passionate team of musicians, engineers and other amazing talents.

Follow us on all of our socials- @behringer for all channels.
